quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Nditsuba khu ing’ining’ini olwa ikhamuukhanga."
  53,2,"Owashienywe uno shiyakora nohomba shiyakhola kano mukhwitsukhanila tawe."
  53,3,"Ne shaboolanga khubwikombi bubwe tawe."
  53,4,"Halali ni obufimbuli bwafimbulilungwa butswa."
  53,5,"Yechesibwa nende Owamaani amanji."
  53,6,"Owalongwa okhulongwa okhulayi mana nakololokha."
  53,7,"Naye ali ebuleka wa hekulu muno wekulu lia hasi."
  53,8,"Mana nasuta ehambi nende omurumwa, ne nameta khandi okhusuta ehambi."
  53,9,"Naba shinga oburambi bwa akari wetsimbeka tsibili tsiatsiyingo tsibiri nohomba ahambi muno."
  53,10,"Mana namufimbulila Omusumba wuwe kalia akayafimbula."
  53,11,"Omwoyo shikwaboola obubeyi khukakwalola tawe."
  53,12,"Koo, mumuyingasinjia khukayalola?"
  53,13,"Mana toto (Omurumwa) yamulolakhwo (Jibril) khandi."
  53,14,"Mushisina shio musaala (mkunazi) kwokhumalilikha muno (omusala kuno kuli mwikulu lia msafu)."
  53,15,"Ahambi nende omusaala oko, kuliwo omukunda kwomwikulu kwamenywamwo."
  53,16,"Olwa kwafimbwa omusaala oko (khubunyali bwa Nyasaye) nende shiakufiimba (shilamanyishe mbu ni shina halali Nyasaye butswa niumanile)."
  53,17,"Tsimoni shitsiesundukha tawe nohomba shitsiabura eshichelo tawe."
  53,18,"Toto yalola khubimanyisio ebikhongo bia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi."
  53,19,"Koo, mwalolakhwo Laata nende Uzza?"
  53,20,"Nende Manata, owundi wakhataru?"
  53,21,"Koo, nenywe muli nabasiani Naye ali nabakhaana?"
  53,22,"Toto okho ni okhukaba okhubi muno."
  53,23,"Ako namerasa kamwakulikha enywe nende basenywe, Nyasaye shiyeshiakhwo shiosishiosi khumeera ako tawe. Balondangasa amaparo nende shie mioyo chiabu chienya. Ne toto obulunjifu bwabetsela okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  53,24,"Mbu Omundu anyoolanga shia yekombanga?"
  53,25,"Nyasaye sa niye mwene mwikulu nende eshialo."
  53,26,"Ne ni Abamalaika benga bali mwikulu, abokhusabila khwabu shikhulikhoonya yesiyesi tawe, halali khuwa Nyasaye achamile mana namufuchilila?"
  53,27,"Toto balia balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe balanganga Abamalaika amera keshikhasi."
  53,28,"Ne babula shibamanyile khu ako tawe, balondanga butswa amaparo. Ne toto okhuparirisia shikhukhoonyanga shiosishiosi imbeli wobwatoto tawe."
  53,29,"Lekhana nende ulia uhelesia omukongo ametsulisio kefu, ne shiyenya shosishosi tawe halali obulamu bwokhushialo."
  53,30,"Awo niwo obumanyi bwabo bulira. Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye umanyile muno ulia wakora ehale nende injila ye, naye amanyile muno ulia walunjikha."
  53,31,"Ne nibia Nyasaye bioosi bili mwikulu nende mushialo, kho abarunge betsimbi khukabakholanga ne abakhola amalayi abarunge obulayi."
  53,32,"Balia beikalilanga okhukhola ebionono ebikhongo nende akeshifwabi, halali orwonono orutiti titi. Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi obulesheli bwe nobubambalifu. Ye abamanyile muno, olwa yabaloonga okhurula khuliloba, nende ngamwali mutsinda tsia banyinenywe. Kho muleelole abatswenufu tawe. Ye amanyile muno owamuria."
  53,33,"Koo! Walolakhwo ulia ufutariranga (ulobanga obwisilamu nibwakhamulila)?"
  53,34,"Nayinia shitutu mana niyemana."
  53,35,"Koo, akhali nende obumanyi khu kefisile, mana akalolanga?"
  53,36,"Nohomba shiyabolelwakhwo khukali mubitabu bia Musa."
  53,37,"Nende Ibrahim wosia indache?"
  53,38,"Mbu Omundu shalichinga tsimbi tsiowashie tawe?"
  53,39,"Ne Omundu shalinyoola halali kalia kayakhola."
  53,40,"Ne toto ebikhole bibie bililolekha."
  53,41,"Mana alirungwa omurungo kukwe kwoosi nikwitsule."
  53,42,"Ne toto khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niwo akaliweela."
  53,43,"Ne toto niye ureranga okhutsekha nende okhulila."
  53,44,"Naye toto niye owufwisinjia nende ulamusinjia."
  53,45,"Ne toto ye niye waloonga eshisatsa nende eshikhasi."
  53,46,"Okhurulana nende imwo yolwibulo nimitswa."
  53,47,"Netoto mbu kali khuye okhulamusibwa khandi."
  53,48,"Ne toto niye uyindiasinjia nende ukholanga ebindu okhuhela."
  53,49,"Ne toto niye Nyasaye Omulesi wetsing’ining’ini tsia Shiira (Ing’ining’ini ya abakhayi balaamanga)."
  53,50,"Ne toto niye wasishia A’ad beimbeli."
  53,51,"Nende Tsamudi shibalekhwa tawe."
  53,52,"Nende Abandu ba Nuhu abaliho imbeli. Toto bali ababii muno abatsimbi po."
  53,53,"Nende tsingongo (tsia abandu ba Luti), yatsichingula hekulu mana natsilakasia mafumama."
  53,54,"Nitsifuunikhwa nende biatsifuunikha."
  53,55,"Mana ni emikabo shina chia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi chiokanakananga?"
  53,56,"Uno ni omwikanyilisi, mubekanyilisi beyimbeli."
  53,57,"Inyanga yeyindukho ili hambi."
  53,58,"Owumao wakhaibuula owulali Nyasaye."
  53,59,"Ne amakhuwa kano (Ikurani) nikamuukanga (mbu karula wa Nyasaye)?"
  53,60,"Ne mutsekhanga, ne shimulilanga tawe?"
  53,61,"Nanyu muli mubukoyani?"
  53,62,"Kho re obweni bwenyu hasi khulwa Nyasaye, ne mumulaame."
